US 3:4{
Users will solve shapes 4 and 5 using the formula for the shapes given on the sheet.
If correct input for shape 4 they will be told they entered the correct and shape 5 will show up.
If incorrect for shape 4 they will be told they are incorrect and shape 4 stays up.
If correct input for shape 5 they will be told they entered the correct area and this minigame is over.
If incorrect for shape 5 they will be told they are incorrect and shape 5 stays up.
Unlike the previous shapes, shapes 4 and 5 will be made of multiple shapes to increase the difficulty.
}
